            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                <p>Of Mares Kyrion (son) of John</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" ana="b1">
                <p>If ΡΙΩΝ is taken as a fragment of the name Kyrion, the inscription then refers to
                    one man by both his Aramaic and his Greek name instead of to two men on a single
                    ossuary.</p>
            </div>
